       PROCEDURE       DIVISION.

       ROT-000-000.
           MOVE     ZEROS    TO  ACM-SDI  ACM-DEP  ACM-PGT
                                 ACM-REC  ACM-DEV  ACM-GCP
                                 ACM-PDT  ACM-SDA  ACM-SDD
