           DISPLAY  TLA-001      TLA-002
                    ENT-001      MEN-001.

       ROT-100-000.
           READ     CADBCO   AT  END
                    GO  TO   ROT-200-000.
           ADD      SDI-BCO  TO  ACM-SDI
           ADD      SDI-BCO  TO  ACM-SDA
           ADD      SDI-BCO  TO  ACM-SDD
           DISPLAY  TLA-001
